Adam: A merchant with an obsessive eye for quality arms and armor. He sources only the finest, demanding perfection from his suppliers. He's a shrewd bargainer, but honors his word, expecting those two favors repaid with equal integrity.

Walter: Relentless investigator, driven by an unwavering pursuit of truth. He is the one tasked with unraveling the tangled threads of crime and bringing the guilty to justice, no matter how deeply buried the secrets.
